## Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not capture the full spectrum of opinions and data on immigration reform. The lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the timeliness of the information. Additionally, the focus on U.S.-based organizations may limit the global perspective on immigration reform. Further research could include more diverse viewpoints and recent legislative developments.